      "subject": "Sunny Days Childcare – Weekly Update: February 18, 2025",
      "from": "mcp.test.dki2@gmail.com",
      "date": "Sun, 11 May 2025 16:00:00 +0000",
      "snippet": "Dear Sunny Days Families, We hope you&#39;re all doing well! Here are some highlights from this week at the center: • Collaborative Mural: The children teamed up on a colorful mural that celebrates",
      "body": "Dear Sunny Days Families,\n\nWe hope you’re all doing well! Here are some highlights from this week at the center:\n\n• Collaborative Mural: The children teamed up on a colorful mural that celebrates friendship and cooperation. Stop by the art wall in the lobby to take a look—everyone is so proud of their work!\n\n• Building Empathy & Support: In our ongoing conversations about feelings and community, many children shared thoughtful insights about supporting one another. We’re always inspired by their kindness.\n\n• Coming Soon – Buddy System: To nurture even stronger peer connections, we’ll be starting a “Buddy System.” Each child will be paired with a friend for shared activities, helping them build confidence and practice teamwork. We’ll send more details, including how you can support at home, next week.\n\nReminders:\n• Please send a labeled water bottle every day.\n• Friday is our Pajama Day – children may wear PJs and bring a favorite book to share.\n\nThank you for your continued partnership. Feel free to reach out with any questions.\n\nWarmly,\n[Your Name]\nDirector, Sunny Days Childcare\n"
